{"id": 1215, "genre": 1000, "title": "在吃东西这件事情上，你都在做着哪些减法？", "description": "为了健康做的食物断舍离，我连泡面都只吃半包。（题图来自：林小妖）", "record_count": 5174, "comment_count": 41, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160914154111XotOrJny8iW4cmYE.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-25T17:00:05Z", "questions": [{"id": 1100, "title": "在吃东西这件事情上，你都在做着哪些减法？", "content": "在吃东西这件事情上，你都在做着哪些减法？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 115298, "content": "喜欢小包装食物", "image": "img/option/option/20160912190504TJKd9LBzjCZOEh5w.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 115299, "content": "给自己制定轻食食谱，一次只吃七八分饱", "image": "img/option/option/20160912190546XaO2YFrdfVn19cCz.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 115300, "content": "尽量不吃油腻的外卖，会自己做少油少盐水煮便当", "image": "img/option/option/20160912191250zMid0p1IxRwECyYt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 115301, "content": "一定要喝酒，会喝淡啤以及“软饮化”的酒", "image": "img/option/option/20160912191029yDSz1l3xYhGPqKwZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 115302, "content": "饮料也要喝低卡路里（100 卡及以下）的或者轻口味水", "image": "img/option/option/201609121914470MI9OSPKHodCzTae.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 115303, "content": "零食偏爱不含人工甜味剂和防腐剂那种", "image": "img/option/option/20160912191240iAlGpch0rZLsuIzg.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 115305, "content": "方便面的调料只放半包，方便面只吃一半", "image": "img/option/option/201609121907067kJTCr10qzUxR8Zi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 115307, "content": "拒绝深加工食物，比如鸡肉丸子、肉罐头之类的", "image": "img/option/option/20160912190910bmWGnIsK6RVtEg9w.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}